  <summary>1/3/2001--Introduced.
Mortgage Servicing Clarification Act - Amends the Fair Debt Collection Practices Act to exempt a servicer of federally related mortgage loans secured by first liens from certain debt collection disclosure requirements if such servicer is a debt collector whose primary function is servicing such loans.</summary>
